    "body" : "<p>You have two options:</p>\n\n<ol>\n<li><p>Define a named class.  Pass your parameter to the constructor of the named class.</p></li>\n<li><p>Have your anonymous class close over your \"parameter\".  Be sure to mark it as <code>final</code>.</p></li>\n</ol>\n"
