    "body" : "<p>I would first want to know what you are trying to accomplish here to need an argument to be passed to new Runnable() or to run().\nThe usual way should be to have a Runnable object which passes data(str) to its threads by setting member variables before starting. The run() method then uses these member variable values to do execute someFunc()</p>\n"
