    "body" : "<pre><code>theView.post(new Runnable() {\n    String str;\n    @Override                            \n    public void run() {\n        par.Log(str);                              \n    }\n    public Runnable init(String pstr) {\n        this.str=pstr;\n        return(this);\n    }\n}.init(str));\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Create init function that returns object itself and initialize parameters with it.</p>\n"
