      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "If still using Runnable with lambda in Java 8, we can do as below: <code>void doSomething(String param) { CompletableFuture.runAsync(() -&gt; howToDo(param));} private void howToDo(String param) { System.out.println(param);}</code>"
